  "title": "*Entry Level* Marketing Executive (Learning Centre) #NJN",
  "description": "<p>Paya Lebar<br />9am to 6pm</p><p><u><strong>Responsibilities & Duties</strong></u></p><ul><li>Support marketing campaigns planning and execution</li><li>Research industry-related topics and prepare well-drafted drafts or copy for social media posts, promotional emails and other marketing collaterals</li><li>Design or assist in the creation of written, video, and image content for marketing channels to advertise our company and products</li><li>Manage social media channels including Instagram, Facebook, Xiao Hong Shu, WeChat, Tik Tok and assist in replying to any customer inquiries</li><li>Ensure the collaterals created are consistent with the branding guidelines</li><li>Design customer success initiatives, or community events like fireside chats for customer engagement through Whatsapp channel</li><li>Plan lead generation events with key partners</li><li>Measure and report the results of marketing campaigns, social media ads and initiatives</li><li>Assists in any other ad-hoc data entry or administrative tasks as requested by the management</li><li>Design and lead team in offline marketing efforts (such as banners, pillar ads) and exhibitions</li></ul><p><u><strong>Requirements</strong></u></p><ul><li>Degree in Marketing</li><li>Knows how to use Photoshop or Illustrator or photo editing software is a plus, but not compulsory</li><li>Knows basic video editing</li></ul><p><br />Jessica Nguyen Huynh Thanh Truc</p><p>CEI Reg. No. R23113787</p><p>EA License No. 99C4599</p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p>",
